{
  "page": "Girl bought to please the king",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Girl bought to please the king</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>girl bought to please the king</b> is one of <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a>'s slaves in <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio%27s_manse\" title=\"Illyrio&#39;s manse\">his manse</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Her given name is not mentioned.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_the_girl\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by the girl</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_the_girl\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about the girl</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_character\">Appearance and character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Girl_bought_to_please_the_king&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The girl is blond, blue-eyed, fair, and willowy.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> She is a talkative girl, sixteen years of age, and is the favorite of <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Girl_bought_to_please_the_king&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The girl was trained as a <a href=\"/index.php/Pillow_house\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pillow house\">bed slave</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a> and was taught the <a href=\"/index.php/Common_Tongue\" title=\"Common Tongue\">Common Tongue</a> at some point. She was bought to please the king, <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a>'s one-time guest <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a>, in the bedchamber.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Girl_bought_to_please_the_king&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Girl_bought_to_please_the_king&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The girl and an older woman help bathe <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> before the princess's introduction to <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>. The young servant is envious that Daenerys will marry the powerful <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">khal</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Girl_bought_to_please_the_king&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After drinking at <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio%27s_manse\" title=\"Illyrio&#39;s manse\">Illyrio's manse</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> wakes to find the girl tending to him, having been told by Magister <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> to bathe the dwarf and warm his bed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Tyrion initially declines the girl's offer to sleep together. After thinking of the girl's revulsion for him, however, Tyrion reconsiders and disparages the girl.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> When he joins Illyrio for supper, Tyrion tells the magister that the girl did all that was required of her.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_the_girl\">Quotes by the girl</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Girl_bought_to_please_the_king&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by the girl\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Now you look all a princess.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;the girl, to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>girl</b>: My name—<br />\n</p><p><b>Tyrion</b>: —is of no interest to me. Do you know where <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitution\" title=\"Prostitution\">whores</a> go?<br />\n<b>Girl</b>: Whores sell themselves for coin.<br />\n<b>Tyrion</b>: Or jewels, or gowns, or castles. But where do they go?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Girl</b>: Is it a riddle, m'lord? I'm no good at riddles.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;the girl and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_the_girl\">Quotes about the girl</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Girl_bought_to_please_the_king&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about the girl\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>She despises me, he realized, but no more than I despise myself.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>It might please m'lord to strangle you. That's how I served <a href=\"/index.php/Shae\" title=\"Shae\">my last whore</a>. Do you think <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">your master</a> would object? Surely not. He has a hundred more like you, but no one else like me.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> to the girl</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>She was trained in <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>, where they make an art of love. <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">The king</a> enjoyed her greatly.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Girl_bought_to_please_the_king&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.7</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\">1.8</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\">1.9</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_1\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 1\">Chapter 1</a>, Tyrion I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_3\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 3\">Chapter 3</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403113121\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.107 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.312 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1448/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11040/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 10648/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1658/2097